-- Toyota U.S. sales down 11.5 pct adjusted
-- 
-- Tue Jul 1, 2008 3:44pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/01/us-usasales-toyota-idUSN0127435320080701

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Co on Tuesday reported an 11.5 percent fall in June U.S. auto sales compared with the same month a year earlier, to 193,234 vehicles. 

 Toyota said its Toyota-brand sales were down 10.3 percent. Sales for its luxury Lexus brand fell 21.1 percent. (Reporting by  Poornima Gupta ; editing by John Wallace)